<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Join Consultation Room</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }
    
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2a6c, #b21f1f, #fdbb2d);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 500px;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #2c3e50, #4ca1af);
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    
    .header p {
      font-size: 16px;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
    
    .join-form {
      padding: 30px;
    }
    
    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .form-group label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
    
    .form-group input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 15px;
      border: 2px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }
    
    .form-group input:focus {
      border-color: #4ca1af;
      outline: none;
    }
    
    .btn {
      padding: 12px 25px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    
    .btn-join {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #00b09b, #96c93d);
      color: white;
    }
    
    .btn-create {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #4ca1af, #2c3e50);
      color: white;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    .btn:active {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    
    .info-box {
      background-color: #e9ecef;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    
    .info-box h3 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      padding-bottom: 8px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #4ca1af;
    }
    
    .info-item {
      margin: 8px 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    
    .info-item span:first-child {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #555;
    }
    
    .message {
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 10px 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .success {
      background-color: #d4edda;
      color: #155724;
      border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
    }
    
    .error {
      background-color: #f8d7da;
      color: #721c24;
      border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
    }
    
    .instruction {
      background-color: #e8f4f8;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    
    .instruction h3 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    .instruction ol {
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    
    .instruction li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Join Consultation Room</h1>
      <p>Enter room ID to connect with your doctor/patient</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="join-form">
      <% if (success && success.length > 0) { %>
        <div class="message success"><%= success %></div>
      <% } %>
      
      <% if (error && error.length > 0) { %>
        <div class="message error"><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>
      
      <form action="/join-room" method="POST">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="roomId"><i class="fas fa-door-open"></i> Room ID</label>
          <input type="text" id="roomId" name="roomId" placeholder="Enter room ID (e.g. DR5429)" required autocomplete="off">
        </div>
        
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="userName"><i class="fas fa-user"></i> Your Name</label>
          <input type="text" id="userName" name="userName" placeholder="Enter your name" required autocomplete="off">
        </div>
        
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-join">
          <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Join Room
        </button>
      </form>
      
      <a href="/create-room">
        <button class="btn btn-create">
          <i class="fas fa-plus"></i> Create New Room
        </button>
      </a>
      
      <div class="instruction">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> How to connect:</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>To create a consultation: Click "Create New Room" and share the Room ID with the other person</li>
          <li>To join a consultation: Enter the Room ID provided by the host and click "Join Room"</li>
          <li>Once connected, you'll be able to start a video call</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      
      <div class="info-box">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Tips for better connection</h3>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span>Stable Internet:</span>
          <span>Required</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span>Webcam & Mic:</span>
          <span>Enable when prompted</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span>Chrome/Firefox:</span>
          <span>Recommended</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>